text: Untrinilium is a hypothetical Element on the periodic table with the honorary name Untrinilium, atomic number of 130, and atomic symbol Utn. Until it is given a permanent name, it will be hypothetical. it is also predicted to be in the Periodic Table's Superactinide series. ==Realated Pages== Unbiennium-- Untriunium Category:Hypothetical chemical elements
title: Untrinilium
